---
import PageLayout from '../../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import CTASection from '../../components/CTASection.astro';
---

<PageLayout
  title="How to Reduce Currency Risks After Brexit | Case Study"
  description="How Gymnamo used a new approach to reduce currency risks stemming from Brexit and customs-related delays."
>
  <section class="section-padding">
    <div class="container-content max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <!-- Breadcrumb -->
      <nav class="mb-8 text-[0.875rem] text-text-muted">
        <a href="/case-studies" class="hover:text-brand-green transition-colors">Case Studies</a>
        <span class="mx-2">/</span>
        <span class="text-text-heading font-medium">Gymnamo</span>
      </nav>

      <!-- Tags -->
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4">
        <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-brand-green-pale text-brand-green text-[0.8125rem] font-semibold rounded-full">
          E-Commerce
        </span>
        <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 text-text-muted text-[0.8125rem] font-medium rounded-full">
          Risk Management
        </span>
      </div>

      <h1 class="text-[2rem] md:text-[2.5rem] font-bold text-text-heading leading-tight mb-4">
        Keeping products affordable for UK rhythmic gymnasts
      </h1>
      <p class="text-[1.25rem] text-brand-green font-semibold mb-10">Gymnamo</p>

      <!-- Pull Quote -->
      <blockquote class="my-10 p-8 bg-brand-green-pale rounded-xl border-l-4 border-brand-green">
        <p class="text-[1.125rem] text-text-heading leading-relaxed italic">
          &ldquo;HedgeFlows gave me the autonomy I needed. No more calls from FX brokers — your system makes it so easy to follow the rates and book them in advance. The last order has saved me 7% as the Pound collapsed. If it hadn't been for this pre-booking, I'd have had to raise my prices in the shop.&rdquo;
        </p>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mt-4">
          <img src="https://8698300.hs-sites.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Inna%20Photo%20RG.jpg?width=96&name=Inna%20Photo%20RG.jpg" alt="Inna, founder of Gymnamo" class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full object-cover" loading="lazy" />
          <cite class="text-[0.9375rem] text-text-body not-italic font-medium">
            &mdash; Inna, Founder
          </cite>
        </div>
      </blockquote>

      <!-- Content Sections -->
      <div class="mb-12">
        <span class="text-[0.75rem] font-semibold text-brand-green uppercase tracking-wider">THE COMPANY</span>
        <h2 class="text-[1.375rem] font-bold text-text-heading mt-1 mb-4 flex items-center gap-3">
          <span class="w-1.5 h-7 bg-brand-green rounded-full inline-block"></span>
          Imported high-quality rhythmic gymnastics gear
        </h2>
        <div class="prose prose-body">
          <p>Gymnamo is the UK's leading specialist shop for rhythmic gymnastics.</p>
<p>The best equipment comes from manufacturers in Japan, Italy, and Spain, while training gear, leotards for competitions and accessories are all made in Europe. Gymnamo makes these products available at affordable prices to consumers in the UK.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-12">
        <span class="text-[0.75rem] font-semibold text-brand-green uppercase tracking-wider">THE PROBLEM</span>
        <h2 class="text-[1.375rem] font-bold text-text-heading mt-1 mb-4 flex items-center gap-3">
          <span class="w-1.5 h-7 bg-brand-green rounded-full inline-block"></span>
          Brexit changed the game
        </h2>
        <div class="prose prose-body">
          <p>Before Brexit, Gymnamo could order small quantities regularly, but due to the new customs rules, the team had to adapt — ordering less frequently but in larger quantities.</p>
<p>Due to the larger currency amounts involved, longer delays and ongoing volatility over the last few years, Inna had to look for a solution that helps her keep costs and, consequently prices in Pounds Sterling stable.</p>
<p>Inna often knew she would need to buy Euros and Dollars for upcoming orders. But she could never fix an exchange rate until she placed her order — even if she knew the rate worked for her margins. If currencies moved too much she had to wait with her order, hoping to keep her prices and margins where she wanted them to be.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-12">
        <span class="text-[0.75rem] font-semibold text-brand-green uppercase tracking-wider">THE SOLUTION</span>
        <h2 class="text-[1.375rem] font-bold text-text-heading mt-1 mb-4 flex items-center gap-3">
          <span class="w-1.5 h-7 bg-brand-green rounded-full inline-block"></span>
          The new approach
        </h2>
        <div class="prose prose-body">
          <p>Booking exchange rates in advance with HedgeFlows solved the problem for Gymnamo. As Inna prepares her purchase orders, she uses HedgeFlows to track exchange rates automatically. When rates reach her target, she can easily book the guaranteed exchange in advance without having to block any of her cash.</p>
<p>A few weeks or months later, she uses the booked rate to pay the invoiced amounts for the placed orders.</p>
        </div>
        <figure class="mt-6">
          <img src="https://8698300.hs-sites.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Rateslevel.png?width=500&name=Rateslevel.png" alt="HedgeFlows rate tracking" class="mx-auto rounded-xl shadow-sm max-w-[280px]" loading="lazy" />
          <figcaption class="mt-2 text-[0.8125rem] text-text-muted text-center">Track rates and book exchanges in advance</figcaption>
        </figure>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-12">
        <span class="text-[0.75rem] font-semibold text-brand-green uppercase tracking-wider">THE IMPACT</span>
        <h2 class="text-[1.375rem] font-bold text-text-heading mt-1 mb-4 flex items-center gap-3">
          <span class="w-1.5 h-7 bg-brand-green rounded-full inline-block"></span>
          Prebooking currencies to keep prices affordable
        </h2>
        <div class="prose prose-body">
          <p><strong>Securing the right exchange rate</strong> &mdash; HedgeFlows gave Inna the autonomy she needed. No more calls from FX brokers — the system makes it easy to follow rates and book them in advance. It costs almost nothing to book an exchange rate in advance.</p>
<p><strong>Saving money and keeping prices affordable</strong> &mdash; The last order saved Gymnamo 7% as the Pound collapsed. Without pre-booking, Inna would have had to raise prices in the shop. Now she can keep products affordable for UK rhythmic gymnasts while protecting her margins.</p>
        </div>
      </div>



      <div class="mt-12">
        <a href="/case-studies" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-brand-green font-semibold hover:gap-3 transition-all">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 rotate-180" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6" />
          </svg>
          Back to case studies
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <CTASection
    headline="Want similar results for your business?"
    primaryCta={{ label: 'Book a Treasury Review', href: '/treasury-health-check' }}
  />
</PageLayout>
